text: Lord Allan Jay Quinto Velasco (born November 9, 1977) is a Filipino politician and lawyer. He has been the Speaker of the House of Representatives since October 12, 2020. He is the Representative of Marinduque's lone district since 2016. He held the same office from 2010 to 2013. ==References== Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:Speakers of the House of Representatives of the Philippines Category:Politicians from Mimaropa Category:Marinduque
